<paragraph blockId="16.[136,1452,482,1373]" pageId="16" pageNumber="77">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,335,1166,1192]" pageId="16" pageNumber="77">Distribution</emphasis>
:—Endemic to the Atlantic Forest Biome of 
<collectingCountry box="[837,905,1166,1192]" name="Brazil" pageId="16" pageNumber="77">Brazil</collectingCountry>
where it occurs from the state of 
<collectingRegion box="[1287,1352,1166,1192]" country="Brazil" name="Bahia" pageId="16" pageNumber="77">Bahia</collectingRegion>
to 
<collectingRegion country="Brazil" name="Santa Catarina" pageId="16" pageNumber="77">Santa Catarina</collectingRegion>
(Goldenberg 2012).
</paragraph>
